---
// src/components/Packages.astro
---

<section id="packages" class="packages">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>Work With Us</h2>
      <p>Scoped engagements with clear deliverables</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tiers-grid">
      <div class="service-tier service-tier--free">
        <div class="tier-top">
          <h3>Free Consult</h3>
          <p class="pricing">Free</p>
          <p class="timing">1 hour</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-body">
          <ul>
            <li>1-on-1 conversation with Ben Medcalf</li>
            <li>Assess fit for AI, graph databases, or automation</li>
            <li>Actionable recommendation: build, wait, or look elsewhere</li>
            <li>Rough scope and effort estimate if there's a fit</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="best-for">
            <strong>Best for:</strong> Figuring out if we're the right partner — zero
            risk.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="https://calendar.app.google/jzac8cPcXKKtnVQ39"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="tier-cta">Book a Free Hour</a
        >
      </div>

      <div class="service-tier">
        <div class="tier-top">
          <h3>Discovery Sprint</h3>
          <p class="pricing">$3k</p>
          <p class="timing">fixed · 1&ndash;2 weeks</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-body">
          <ul>
            <li>Technical feasibility assessment</li>
            <li>Architecture recommendation</li>
            <li>Scope & estimate for build phase</li>
            <li>Written deliverable you own</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="best-for">
            <strong>Best for:</strong> Validating an idea before committing budget.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="https://calendar.app.google/jzac8cPcXKKtnVQ39"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="tier-cta">Book a Discovery Sprint</a
        >
      </div>

      <div class="service-tier">
        <div class="tier-top">
          <h3>Build Sprint</h3>
          <p class="pricing">$6k&ndash;$15k</p>
          <p class="timing">fixed · 2&ndash;6 weeks</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-body">
          <ul>
            <li>End-to-end implementation</li>
            <li>Testing & validation suite</li>
            <li>Deployment & monitoring</li>
            <li>Training & documentation</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="best-for">
            <strong>Best for:</strong> Shipping a scoped feature or integration.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="https://calendar.app.google/jzac8cPcXKKtnVQ39"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="tier-cta">Start a Build Sprint</a
        >
      </div>

      <div class="service-tier">
        <div class="tier-top">
          <h3>Retainer</h3>
          <p class="pricing">$2k+</p>
          <p class="timing">monthly · ongoing</p>
        </div>
        <div class="tier-body">
          <ul>
            <li>Support for what we shipped</li>
            <li>Code reviews from who wrote it</li>
            <li>Priority when you're ready for the next sprint</li>
            <li>Same-day async responses</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="best-for">
            <strong>Best for:</strong> Teams who want to keep building with MSS.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a
          href="https://calendar.app.google/jzac8cPcXKKtnVQ39"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="tier-cta">Get Started</a
        >
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="how-it-works">
      <h3>How It Works</h3>
      <p>Go in order, mix and match, or pick just one. Up to you.</p>
      <div class="steps-flow">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">1</span>
          <strong>Free Consultation</strong>
          <span class="step-desc"
            >You book a free call with us to see if we're a fit.</span
          >
        </div>
        <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">2</span>
          <strong>Discovery Sprint</strong>
          <span class="step-desc"
            >We define roadmaps unique to your goals and budget</span
          >
        </div>
        <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">3</span>
          <strong>Build Sprint</strong>
          <span class="step-desc"
            >We execute and build something great together</span
          >
        </div>
        <span class="step-arrow">→</span>
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">4</span>
          <strong>Retainer</strong>
          <span class="step-desc"
            >You keep us around for any ongoing support or maintenance</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .packages {
    padding: 100px 0;
    background: #f8f9fa;
  }

  .tiers-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 5rem;
  }

  .service-tier {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 15px;
    padding: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition:
      transform 0.3s ease,
      box-shadow 0.3s ease,
      outline-color 0.3s ease;
    text-align: center;
    overflow: hidden;
    outline: 1px solid rgba(35, 170, 87, 0.15);
  }

  .service-tier:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(35, 170, 87, 0.2);
    outline: 2px solid #23aa57;
  }

  .service-tier--free {
    background: white;
  }

  .tier-top {
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem 1.25rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .service-tier h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: #333;
    margin: 0 0 0.75rem 0;
  }

  .pricing {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #23aa57;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }

  .timing {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #888;
    margin: 0.25rem 0 0;
  }

  .tier-body {
    padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 1rem;
    flex: 1;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .service-tier ul {
    margin: 0 0 1.25rem;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  .service-tier li {
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .service-tier li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #23aa57;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .best-for {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #555;
    margin: 0;
    padding-top: 1rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .best-for strong {
    color: #333;
  }

  .tier-cta {
    display: block;
    margin: auto 1.5rem 1.5rem;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #23aa57 0%, #16a05a 100%);
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    text-align: center;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .tier-cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(29, 191, 115, 0.3);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #28bd62 0%, #18b065 100%);
  }

  /* How It Works — horizontal left-to-right flow */
  .how-it-works {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .how-it-works h3 {
    color: #333;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .how-it-works > p {
    color: #666;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .steps-flow {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: stretch;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .step {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem 1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    outline: 1px solid rgba(35, 170, 87, 0.15);
  }

  .step-number {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #23aa57;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .step strong {
    color: #333;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .step-desc {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .step-arrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: #23aa57;
    font-size: 1.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .tiers-grid {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .tiers-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    .steps-flow {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .step-arrow {
      transform: rotate(90deg);
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
